{"id":"ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE","title":"Simple CDS View — Basic SELECT from a database table","phase":1,"phaseName":"Fundamentals","category":"Fundamentals","subcategory":"Getting Started","language":"abap","description":"Simple CDS View — Basic SELECT from a database table. Key topics: @AbapCatalog.sqlViewName   → Technical SQL view name visible in SE11. @AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter → Optimizes WHERE clause filtering. @AbapCatalog.preserveKey   → Preserves key fields as defined.","sections":[{"title":"Key Learning Points","description":"<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName   → Technical SQL view name visible in SE11</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter → Optimizes WHERE clause filtering</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@AbapCatalog.preserveKey   → Preserves key fields as defined</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@AccessControl.authorizationCheck → #CHECK / #NOT_REQUIRED / #NOT_ALLOWED</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@EndUserText.label         → Description text (SE11, ADT)</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@Environment.systemField:#CLIENT → Client field mapping for implicit WHERE</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@Semantics annotations     → Define semantic meaning for fields</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>define view { entity_name } → CDS entity name used in ABAP/openSQL</span></div></div>"},{"title":"Concept Diagram","description":"<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 750\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"a\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"1000\" height=\"55\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">CDS View Syntax — Complete Breakdown</text>\n\n  <!-- Full code example -->\n  <rect x=\"30\" y=\"70\" width=\"940\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"90\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_SIMPLE'                    <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 1. Annotation block</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"105\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter: true                       <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 2. View metadata</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"120\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK                       <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 3. Access control</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@EndUserText.label: 'Simple Example View'                       <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 4. UI labeling</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"155\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#22C55E\">define view ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE                                    <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 5. View definition</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"170\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  as select from /dmo/travel                                    <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 6. Data source</tspan></text>\n\n  <!-- Annotations detail -->\n  <rect x=\"30\" y=\"190\" width=\"460\" height=\"160\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FFF3ED\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"212\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">1–4  Annotations (Metadata)</text>\n  <line x1=\"50\" y1=\"218\" x2=\"470\" y2=\"218\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"238\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName</tspan>  → SQL view name in HANA</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"256\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter</tspan>  → Push filter to source</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"274\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@AccessControl.authorizationCheck</tspan>  → #CHECK / #NOT_REQ / #PRIVILEGED_ONLY</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"292\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@EndUserText.label</tspan>  → Display name in Fiori / ADT</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"310\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@Semantics.amount.currencyCode</tspan>  → Currency reference</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"328\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">@Search.searchable: true  → Enable search (OData)</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"346\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">@Consumption.* / @UI.*  → Fiori UI annotations</text>\n\n  <!-- View definition detail -->\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"190\" width=\"460\" height=\"160\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#E0F2FE\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"212\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">5–6  View Declaration</text>\n  <line x1=\"530\" y1=\"218\" x2=\"950\" y2=\"218\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"238\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">define view</tspan>  → Keyword declares a CDS view</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"256\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</tspan>  → View name (use naming convention)</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"274\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">as select from</tspan>  → Source = CDS view or DDIC table</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"292\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">/dmo/travel</tspan>  → Fully qualified entity name</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"310\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">You can also use: alias (as _Alias)</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"328\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Projection: use define view entity</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"346\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Parameters: (param: type) after view name</text>\n\n  <!-- Field list -->\n  <rect x=\"30\" y=\"370\" width=\"940\" height=\"120\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"392\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">{                                                <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 7. Field list opens</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"410\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#EAB308\">  key travel_id          as TravelId,            <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 8. Key element</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"428\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">      agency_id          as AgencyId,</text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"446\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">      customer_id        as CustomerId,</text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"464\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">      total_price         as TotalPrice,</text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"482\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#3B82F6\">      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'  <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 9. Field-level annotation</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"500\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">      booking_fee        as BookingFee</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"520\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">}                                                <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 10. Field list closes</tspan></text>\n\n  <!-- Field list explanation -->\n  <rect x=\"30\" y=\"505\" width=\"940\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"527\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">7–10  Field Selection List</text>\n  <line x1=\"50\" y1=\"533\" x2=\"950\" y2=\"533\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"553\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#EAB308\">7.</tspan> <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">{ }</tspan>  → Curly braces enclose the selected elements</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"571\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#EAB308\">8.</tspan> <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">key</tspan>  → Marks primary key (CAN be omitted for views based on other views)</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"589\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#EAB308\">9.</tspan> <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">as</tspan>  → Alias for the output field name (recommended: CamelCase)</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"607\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#EAB308\">10.</tspan> Field-level annotations  → @Semantics, @UI, @Consumption placed BEFORE the field</text>\n\n  <!-- Association + filter section -->\n  <rect x=\"30\" y=\"625\" width=\"940\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"647\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Extended Syntax — Associations, Joins, Filters, Parameters</text>\n  <line x1=\"50\" y1=\"653\" x2=\"950\" y2=\"653\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"673\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#A855F7\">association</tspan> [0..1] to /dmo/agency as _Agency on $projection.AgencyId = _Agency.agency_id</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"693\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#A855F7\">inner / left outer / right outer / cross join</tspan>  → Join other entities in SELECT</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"713\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#A855F7\">where</tspan> Status = 'A'  → Filter condition (can use params: $parameters.param_name)</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"733\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#A855F7\">with parameters</tspan> (p_carrid: /dmo/carrier-carrier_id)  → Input parameters before SELECT</text>\n</svg></div>"},{"title":"CDS Source Code","language":"abap","codeBlock":"@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_SIMPLE'\n@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter: true\n@AbapCatalog.preserveKey: true\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\n@EndUserText.label: 'Practice CDS - Simple SELECT from /dmo/travel'\ndefine view ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE\n  as select from /dmo/travel\n{\n  @Environment.systemField: #CLIENT\n  key client            as Client,\n  key travel_id         as TravelId,\n      agency_id         as AgencyId,\n      customer_id       as CustomerId,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      begin_date        as BeginDate,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      end_date          as EndDate,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      booking_fee       as BookingFee,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      total_price       as TotalPrice,\n      currency_code     as CurrencyCode,\n      description       as Description,\n      status            as Status,\n      @Semantics.user.createdBy: true\n      createdby         as Createdby,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      createdat         as Createdat,\n      @Semantics.user.lastChangedBy: true\n      lastchangedby     as Lastchangedby,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      lastchangedat     as Lastchangedat\n}"}],"content":"<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE-key-learning-points\">Key Learning Points</h2>\n<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName   → Technical SQL view name visible in SE11</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter → Optimizes WHERE clause filtering</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@AbapCatalog.preserveKey   → Preserves key fields as defined</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@AccessControl.authorizationCheck → #CHECK / #NOT_REQUIRED / #NOT_ALLOWED</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@EndUserText.label         → Description text (SE11, ADT)</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@Environment.systemField:#CLIENT → Client field mapping for implicit WHERE</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@Semantics annotations     → Define semantic meaning for fields</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>define view { entity_name } → CDS entity name used in ABAP/openSQL</span></div></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE-concept-diagram\">Concept Diagram</h2>\n<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 750\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"a\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"1000\" height=\"55\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">CDS View Syntax — Complete Breakdown</text>\n\n  <!-- Full code example -->\n  <rect x=\"30\" y=\"70\" width=\"940\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"90\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_SIMPLE'                    <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 1. Annotation block</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"105\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter: true                       <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 2. View metadata</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"120\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK                       <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 3. Access control</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@EndUserText.label: 'Simple Example View'                       <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 4. UI labeling</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"155\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#22C55E\">define view ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE                                    <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 5. View definition</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"170\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  as select from /dmo/travel                                    <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 6. Data source</tspan></text>\n\n  <!-- Annotations detail -->\n  <rect x=\"30\" y=\"190\" width=\"460\" height=\"160\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FFF3ED\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"212\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">1–4  Annotations (Metadata)</text>\n  <line x1=\"50\" y1=\"218\" x2=\"470\" y2=\"218\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"238\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName</tspan>  → SQL view name in HANA</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"256\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter</tspan>  → Push filter to source</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"274\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@AccessControl.authorizationCheck</tspan>  → #CHECK / #NOT_REQ / #PRIVILEGED_ONLY</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"292\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@EndUserText.label</tspan>  → Display name in Fiori / ADT</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"310\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@Semantics.amount.currencyCode</tspan>  → Currency reference</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"328\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">@Search.searchable: true  → Enable search (OData)</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"346\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">@Consumption.* / @UI.*  → Fiori UI annotations</text>\n\n  <!-- View definition detail -->\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"190\" width=\"460\" height=\"160\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#E0F2FE\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"212\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">5–6  View Declaration</text>\n  <line x1=\"530\" y1=\"218\" x2=\"950\" y2=\"218\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"238\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">define view</tspan>  → Keyword declares a CDS view</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"256\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</tspan>  → View name (use naming convention)</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"274\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">as select from</tspan>  → Source = CDS view or DDIC table</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"292\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">/dmo/travel</tspan>  → Fully qualified entity name</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"310\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">You can also use: alias (as _Alias)</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"328\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Projection: use define view entity</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"346\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Parameters: (param: type) after view name</text>\n\n  <!-- Field list -->\n  <rect x=\"30\" y=\"370\" width=\"940\" height=\"120\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"392\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">{                                                <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 7. Field list opens</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"410\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#EAB308\">  key travel_id          as TravelId,            <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 8. Key element</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"428\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">      agency_id          as AgencyId,</text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"446\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">      customer_id        as CustomerId,</text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"464\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">      total_price         as TotalPrice,</text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"482\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#3B82F6\">      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'  <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 9. Field-level annotation</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"500\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">      booking_fee        as BookingFee</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"520\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">}                                                <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- 10. Field list closes</tspan></text>\n\n  <!-- Field list explanation -->\n  <rect x=\"30\" y=\"505\" width=\"940\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"527\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">7–10  Field Selection List</text>\n  <line x1=\"50\" y1=\"533\" x2=\"950\" y2=\"533\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"553\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#EAB308\">7.</tspan> <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">{ }</tspan>  → Curly braces enclose the selected elements</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"571\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#EAB308\">8.</tspan> <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">key</tspan>  → Marks primary key (CAN be omitted for views based on other views)</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"589\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#EAB308\">9.</tspan> <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">as</tspan>  → Alias for the output field name (recommended: CamelCase)</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"607\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#EAB308\">10.</tspan> Field-level annotations  → @Semantics, @UI, @Consumption placed BEFORE the field</text>\n\n  <!-- Association + filter section -->\n  <rect x=\"30\" y=\"625\" width=\"940\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"647\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Extended Syntax — Associations, Joins, Filters, Parameters</text>\n  <line x1=\"50\" y1=\"653\" x2=\"950\" y2=\"653\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"673\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#A855F7\">association</tspan> [0..1] to /dmo/agency as _Agency on $projection.AgencyId = _Agency.agency_id</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"693\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#A855F7\">inner / left outer / right outer / cross join</tspan>  → Join other entities in SELECT</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"713\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#A855F7\">where</tspan> Status = 'A'  → Filter condition (can use params: $parameters.param_name)</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"733\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#A855F7\">with parameters</tspan> (p_carrid: /dmo/carrier-carrier_id)  → Input parameters before SELECT</text>\n</svg></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE-cds-source-code\">CDS Source Code</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-abap\">@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_SIMPLE'\n@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter: true\n@AbapCatalog.preserveKey: true\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\n@EndUserText.label: 'Practice CDS - Simple SELECT from /dmo/travel'\ndefine view ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE\n  as select from /dmo/travel\n{\n  @Environment.systemField: #CLIENT\n  key client            as Client,\n  key travel_id         as TravelId,\n      agency_id         as AgencyId,\n      customer_id       as CustomerId,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      begin_date        as BeginDate,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      end_date          as EndDate,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      booking_fee       as BookingFee,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      total_price       as TotalPrice,\n      currency_code     as CurrencyCode,\n      description       as Description,\n      status            as Status,\n      @Semantics.user.createdBy: true\n      createdby         as Createdby,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      createdat         as Createdat,\n      @Semantics.user.lastChangedBy: true\n      lastchangedby     as Lastchangedby,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      lastchangedat     as Lastchangedat\n}</code></pre>","tags":["cds-view"],"details":"<p class=\"mb-2\">USAGE IN ABAP:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">SELECT * FROM ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">INTO TABLE @DATA(lt_travel).</p><p class=\"mb-2\">SELECT TravelId, AgencyId, TotalPrice</p><p class=\"mb-2\">FROM ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">INTO TABLE @DATA(lt_travel_short)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">WHERE CustomerId = '000115'.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DIAGRAM: assets/diagrams/cds-syntax.svg</p>","cdsViewName":"ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE","sqlViewName":"ZPRAC_SQL_SIMPLE","topic":"Foundation — all CDS views build on this pattern"}